data.description: This charming home sits on a spacious .82-acre lot in a serene country setting, offering tranquility and privacy. Impeccably maintained, it boasts a move-in ready condition, perfect for those eager to settle into their new abode without delay.  The heart of the home is its expansive, open-concept eat-in kitchen, complete with all appliances, ensuring both functionality and convenience for cooking and dining experiences. A dedicated laundry room adds to the practicality of daily living.  The living room provides a welcoming space for relaxation and entertainment, while the foyer offers a warm and inviting entry point. Enjoy the picturesque views of the surrounding nature from the comfort of the screened porch, providing a peaceful retreat to unwind and enjoy the outdoors.  Step outside to discover the lush, wooded backyard, partially fenced for added privacy and security. A sizable storage building/workshop with electricity further enhances the property's utility, offering ample space for storage or DIY projects.  Experience the joys of country living coupled with modern comforts in this delightful home, where every detail has been thoughtfully attended to for your utmost enjoyment and convenience.
